Counting days with tallymarks. http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tally_marks
A simple visualization to show big numbers, like for example how long you've been here.
Webfont "Shadows Into Light" by Kimberly Gesweinvia via Google: http://www.google.com/webfonts/specimen/Shadows+Into+Light

1. Read a date from userinput.
2. Calculate the difference to today in days.
3. Render the number of days with tallymarks.


